node_2.subject: Klaus Mueller
node_2.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 8:00 am, start reading the generative agent paper at 8:30 am, take notes and analyze the paper until 9:30 am, prepare the presentation slides based on the paper from 9:30 am to 10:00 am, give the presentation to Isabella Rodriguez and Maria Lopez at 10:00 am, discuss the paper with Isabella and Maria after the presentation, continue working on the paper and make any necessary revisions until 12:00 pm, take a break and have lunch from 12:00 pm to 1:00 pm.
